page.title: 20CREDITS
page.content: THANKS ARE GIVEN TO THE CHILDREN OF THE JUNIOR DEPARTMENT OF STOKE CLIMSLAND SCHOOL FOR ALL THEIR WORK IN PREPARING THE DOOMESDAY MATERIAL, IN PARTICTULAR THE GIRLS OF THE J2 CLASS WHO TYPED IN THE TEXT. PHOTGRAPHS WERE CONTRIBUTED BY C.R.PARSONS, T.J.NORISH, E.L.BAILEY AND NOBODY. THANKS ARE ALSO DUE TO THE PEOPLE WHO WERE KIND ENOUGH TO COMPLETE THE SURVEY FORMS. FINALLY THANKS MUST GO TO ALL THE OTHER PEOPLE OF THE PARISH WHO GAVE SO FREELY THEIR TIME, AND OF THEIR KNOWLEDGE OF THE AREA.
